--- !u!1001 &46065392
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 1342530508445073221, guid: aa30cf7fa2f4d644b9b7b9c416d22508, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Humans are coming to take the magic from the tree of magic!


        drag
        and drop towers from the top left onto sections of the lane to place towers
        and defend the tree.

        Each tower has a magic cost that must be paid
        every second, seen on their profile card (top left)

        Use unicorn
        bunnies to increase your magic gain (but they can only be summoned once every
        30 seconds


        Mouse over a tower and press backspace to destroy a
        tower, you will stop using mana on it as a result.


        Don''t let the
        humans get through and don''t run out of magic!'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1342530508445073221, guid: aa30cf7fa2f4d644b9b7b9c416d22508, type: 3}
